erwaal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bronze medalist\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 950}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 963}, {\"ngram\": \"2024 Olympics\", \"from\": 964, \"to\": 977}, {\"ngram\": \"IrishCentral's newsletter\", \"from\": 1040, \"to\": 1065}, {\"ngram\": \"date\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1084}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1090, \"to\": 1100}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McSharry told RT\\u00c9 Sport on Monday that becoming an Olympic medallist feels \\\"unbelievable.\\\"\", \"from\": 1112, \"to\": 1202, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1126, \"end\": 1135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9999999789533833, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RT\\u00c9 Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9_Sport\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"McSharry\", \"from\": 1112, \"to\": 1120}, {\"ngram\": \"Monday\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1145}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic medallist\", \"from\": 1160, \"to\": 1180}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think there was a moment on the podium where I just started tearing up.\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1278, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a moment\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1231}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1245}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's when it was like, oh s--t, this is really happening,\\\" an emotional McSharry said.\", \"from\": 1279, \"to\": 1367, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"oh s\", \"from\": 1304, \"to\": 1308}, {\"ngram\": \"an emotional McSharry\", \"from\": 1340, \"to\": 1361}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's unbelievable.\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1388, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's been a lot of hard work and I think there is always been a little bit of doubt - do I really belong at the top?\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1505, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1399, \"to\": 1404}, {\"ngram\": \"hard work\", \"from\": 1408, \"to\": 1417}, {\"ngram\": \"a little bit\", \"from\": 1451, \"to\": 1463}, {\"ngram\": \"doubt\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1472}, {\"ngram\": \"the top\", \"from\": 1497, \"to\": 1504}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This proves it.\", \"from\": 1506, \"to\": 1521, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I raced my heart out and to be on the right side of a really tight race is really unbelievable.\\\"\", \"from\": 1523, \"to\": 1620, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my heart\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1540}, {\"ngram\": \"the right side\", \"from\": 1558, \"to\": 1572}, {\"ngram\": \"a really tight race\", \"from\": 1576, \"to\": 1595}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McSharry admitted it wasn't a \\\"perfect\\\" race and that her goggles filled up with water.\", \"from\": 1622, \"to\": 1709, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"McSharry\", \"from\": 1622, \"to\": 1630}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"perfect\\\" race\", \"from\": 1650, \"to\": 1666}, {\"ngram\": \"her goggles\", \"from\": 1676, \"to\": 1687}, {\"ngram\": \"water\", \"from\": 1703, \"to\": 1708}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She continued: \\\"Regardless of the result, even being able to compete at this level and confidently be in with a chance of medalling and then actually medalling - it's just what sport is about - those really tight races and just having fun.\", \"from\": 1711, \"to\": 1950, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the result\", \"from\": 1741, \"to\": 1751}, {\"ngram\": \"this level\", \"from\": 1783, \"to\": 1793}, {\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 1821, \"to\": 1829}, {\"ngram\": \"what sport\", \"from\": 1883, \"to\": 1893}, {\"ngram\": \"those really tight races\", \"from\": 1905, \"to\": 1929}, {\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 1946, \"to\": 1949}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Sometimes it's hard because you are so nervous to really have fun but that's the most important part, just soaking up these moments.\\\"\", \"from\": 1952, \"to\": 2086, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 2015, \"to\": 2018}, {\"ngram\": \"the most important part\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2053}, {\"ngram\": \"these moments\", \"from\": 2071, \"to\": 2084}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McSharry won her Bronze Olympic medal after considering leaving the sport a few years ago.\", \"from\": 2088, \"to\": 2178, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"McSharry\", \"from\": 2088, \"to\": 2096}, {\"ngram\": \"her Bronze Olympic medal\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2125}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 2152, \"to\": 2161}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think almost walking away from the sport really put into perspective why I do it,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2180, \"to\": 2275, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 2214, \"to\": 2223}, {\"ngram\": \"perspective\", \"from\": 2240, \"to\": 2251}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"These are just bonuses, and they are amazing bonuses, but it's all the friends, and the family, and the community that I meet and make along the way and that I get to share these moments with are the most important and that's just unbelievable.\", \"from\": 2277, \"to\": 2522, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just bonuses\", \"from\": 2288, \"to\": 2300}, {\"ngram\": \"amazing bonuses\", \"from\": 2315, \"to\": 2330}, {\"ngram\": \"all the friends\", \"from\": 2341, \"to\": 2356}, {\"ngram\": \"the family\", \"from\": 2362, \"to\": 2372}, {\"ngram\": \"the community\", \"from\": 2378, \"to\": 2391}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 2419, \"to\": 2426}, {\"ngram\": \"these moments\", \"from\": 2451, \"to\": 2464}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And then getting to be a part of tight races and putting yourself in those positions where you are digging deep and pushing really hard is just really fun.\\\"\", \"from\": 2524, \"to\": 2681, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a part\", \"from\": 2548, \"to\": 2554}, {\"ngram\": \"tight races\", \"from\": 2558, \"to\": 2569}, {\"ngram\": \"those positions\", \"from\": 2594, \"to\": 2609}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McSharry added: \\\"I was a little girl from a tiny, little village - and I still am that little girl from Sligo - and I was able to win a medal at the Olympics so it just shows that you can do anything you put your mind to.\\\"\", \"from\": 2683, \"to\": 2905, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2787, \"end\": 2792, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sligo\", \"score\": 0.6527908561589918, \"rank\": 0.48430622379636185, \"text\": \"Sligo\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sligo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sligo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"McSharry\", \"from\": 2683, \"to\": 2691}, {\"ngram\": \"a little girl\", \"from\": 2706, \"to\": 2719}, {\"ngram\": \"a tiny, little village\", \"from\": 2725, \"to\": 2747}, {\"ngram\": \"that little girl\", \"from\": 2765, \"to\": 2781}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 2817, \"to\": 2824}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2828, \"to\": 2840}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 2874, \"to\": 2882}, {\"ngram\": \"your mind\", \"from\": 2891, \"to\": 2900}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am still that little girl from Sligo\\\" ?\", \"from\": 2907, \"to\": 2949, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2941, \"end\": 2946, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sligo\", \"score\": 0.6527908561589918, \"rank\": 0.48430622379636185, \"text\": \"Sligo\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sligo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sligo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that little girl\", \"from\": 2919, \"to\": 2935}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The tears are in full flow as the reality of Olympic bronze sinks in for Mona McSharry#RTESport#Paris2024?Updateshttps://t.co/NhnQoPxaeE?Watchhttps://t.co/b2OI4OoWVJ